These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, dancing, hiking, reading, singing
City: nizza, hamburg, hannover, london, edinburgh
There 5 different types of food: tomato, asparagus, carrot, lime, pineapple
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, juice, iced-tea, lemonade
 1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the person eating asparagus is the person traveling to london##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
11. the person eating asparagus is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | reading | hiking    | singing  |
| City   | hamburg  | nizza | hannover | london | edinburgh  |
| Food           | tomato     | pineapple     | lime  | asparagus   | carrot    |
| Beverage         | juice | iced-tea    | cola | soy-milk  | lemonade |

