.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: mauve, blood-red, red, green, ebony
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, architect, dressmaker, photographer, scientist
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, november, february, august, june
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, cain, pall-mall, ritmeester, prince
 1. the photographer is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the cain-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the scientist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person who likes red is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who likes red##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes green is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
12. the person who likes red is the architect##1
13. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Color          | red        | ebony | blood-red     | green      | mauve  |
| Job           | architect   | dressmaker | scientist    | photographer | accountant |
| Birthday   | february | august     | june | july    | november  |
| Cigar   | ritmeester     | cain | game    | prince      | pall-mall    |

