.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different pets are kept: goat, rat, chinchilla, frog, guinea-pig
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, comedy, drama, crime, mystery
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, lilac, fuchsia, ebony, green
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, scooter, snowmobile, train
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person who likes light-blue is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 9. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
11. the person who likes fuchsia is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
13. the owner of the frog is the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Pet      | frog          | chinchilla  | rat       | goat     | guinea-pig      |
| Movie-Genre         | comedy | mystery | crime  | drama   | horror    |
| Color   | lilac        | green | light-blue | ebony    | fuchsia   |
| Transport     | helicopter   | scooter | train      | quad-bike | snowmobile |

