.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk, juice, iced-tea, water
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, chestnut, light-blue, pink, apricot
The people have 5 different jobs:  paramedic, lawyer, engineer, coach, architect
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, taxi, van
 1. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the paramedic##1
 2. the person who likes red is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the lawyer is the person who likes chestnut##1
 4. the paramedic is the person who likes red##1
 5. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the coach##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the coach is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person drinking water is the engineer##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Beverage          | iced-tea        | soy-milk       | juice | milk   | water  |
| Color   | apricot | light-blue | chestnut | red   | pink |
| Job   | coach         | architect     | lawyer | paramedic | engineer     |
| Transport     | bike        | car        | van    | taxi    | ship      |

