5 different games are played: go, poker, backgammon, domino, mah-jongg
House: craftsman, colonial, art-deco, wooden, victorian
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 2. the art-deco house is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person eating raspberry is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is the person playing go##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing domino is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 9. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person playing domino is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
11. the person who's hobby is photography is the person eating cherry##1
12. the wooden house is the person playing poker##1
13. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |
| Food          | cherry     | lettuce  | raspberry | banana     | artichoke |
