The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, pop, classical, indie, dubstep
 1. the fan of house is the palace house##1
 2. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 3. the fan of house is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the wooden house##1
 6. the wooden house is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of pop is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is the fan of classical##1
10. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
13. the wooden house is on the left of the fan of classical##1
14. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
| House      | palace        | craftsman   | futuristic  | wooden         | ranch-style |
| Hobby   | writing   | puzzles   | baking | video-games      | gardening   |
