 4. the person playing poker is the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the dressmaker is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is the paramedic##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is the paramedic##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is the person watching western movies##1
11. the person playing domino is the accountant##1
12. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person playing poker##1
13. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
