 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who likes lavender##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person watching romance movies is the person traveling to marseilles##1
13. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Sport      | rugby      | rowing       | skiing         | baseball  | soccer |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | scientific | martial-arts | crime  | western  |
| City   | marseilles    | miami    | paris        | boston | san-francisco     |
| Color           | chestnut | blue      | lavender       | aquamarine   | grey   |

