There 5 different types of food: potato, asparagus, cherry, onion, corn
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, french, brazilian, chinese, canadian
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower, daisy, poppy, rose
 1. the french is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 3. the person eating corn is the person who growsbegonia##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the left of the brazilian##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is in the middle##1
10. the canadian is on the right of the brazilian##1
11. the person eating potato is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
12. the person eating cherry is the person drinking tea##1
13. the chinese is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

